data.description: **Gorgeous Pool Home with Solar Efficiency!**  Welcome to your dream retreat! This immaculate property boasts an array of features designed for comfort, convenience, and sustainability. Here's what awaits you:  ** Bedrooms**: Spacious living quarters perfect for relaxation and privacy.  **2 Baths**: Modern amenities to cater to your comfort needs.  **Expansive Property**: Enjoy the luxury of 3/4 acres with the option to expand into the adjacent 1/4 acres property which is listing for sale $16,900.   **Private Pool**: Dive into relaxation and entertainment in your own backyard paradise.   **Open Floor Plan**: Experience seamless flow and versatility in design, ideal for both everyday living and entertaining.   **Equipment Upgrades**: Recent enhancements include a new 50-gallon hot water heater, updated septic tank drain field, lift station (2 yrs old) , deepened well (1 yr ago), upgraded water system, and a state-of-the-art AC system (1 yr old).   **Ceiling Fans**: Stay cool and comfortable throughout the home with seven ceiling fans strategically placed for optimal airflow.   **Storage Shed**: Additional space to store your outdoor equipment and belongings.   **Solar Panels**: Benefit from reduced energy costs with solar efficiency. Take over payments or opt for professional removal, with assurances of roof integrity provided by the seller.   **Energy Savings**: Experience significant savings on your monthly electric bill, with the current bill averaging just $25 per month.    Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this stunning property! Contact the listing agent today to schedule a showing and explore all the possibilities this home has to offer.
